        <section id="home" class = "active">
            <hgroup>
                <h1>Eliminating Systemic Bias in Medical Research and Practice</h1>
                <h2>Why our mission matters for healthcare equality </h2>
            </hgroup>
            <p>
                Systemic bias in medical research and practice has long been a barrier to equitable healthcare. 
                Underrepresentation of certain demographics in clinical trials, biased diagnostic tools, and 
                unequal access to treatments contribute to disparities in health outcomes. At MediBias, we are 
                dedicated to identifying these biases and promoting inclusivity in medical research and practice.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section id="stats">
            <h2>Medical Research Inclusivity Statistics</h2>
            <p>Search our database of recent research data to see female representation levels.</p>
