                <div id="dxQuestions" style="display:none;">
                    <hr>
                    <h5>Follow-up Diagnostic Questions:</h5>
                    <ul>
                        <li>On a scale of 1-10, how debilitating are the menstrual cramps?</li>
                        <li>On a scale of 1-10, how heavy is the bleeding (clotting/duration)?</li>
                        <li>Are secondary symptoms present, such as chronic migraines or lower back pain?</li>
                        <li>How regular is the menstrual cycle, and does pain persist outside of the period?</li>
                        <li>Does the patient experience pain during bowel movements or intercourse?</li>
                    </ul>
                    <small><i>Note: These questions target common signs of Endometriosis often dismissed as "normal" period pain.</i></small>
                </div>
